* Sven witnessed a stranger engage in a drinking contest with a mysterious man named Sam at the Sleeping Giant Inn. The competition drew quite a crowd, and Sven had to compete for attention during his performance.
{% endif %}

{# The aftermath of the Night to Remember quest would be notable to Sven as it involves the Sleeping Giant Inn where he performs. #}
{% if get_quest_stage("DA14", true) >= 10 and get_quest_stage("DA14", true) < 40 %}
* Sven heard from Orgnar that someone woke up in the Temple of Dibella in Markarth after drinking with Sam at the Sleeping Giant. The tale has become a favorite topic among inn patrons.
{% endif %}
{% endblock %}